name: Sound of Fractures - No One Knows Me Like You ft Scott Quinn (Acoustic)

attributes.trait_type: No One Knows Me Like You ft Scott Quinn (Acoustic)

metadata.description:
To celebrate the release of ‘No One Knows Me Like You', we are minting this exclusive acoustic version of the song on sound.xyz. 

The artwork is created from photos submitted by friends, fans, and family around us. 

The photos chosen represent a moment in time for every contributor, us, and the music scene that has been so supportive over the last 6 months.

I hope it connects with you the same way it did with us the day we wrote it x

lyrics.text:
I never wanted you to see me like this 
You look into my eyes and something just clicks 
You see me like nobody else
When I feel like someone else

I never wanted you to hurt like this 
I guess you never do but that’s the way it is
You see right through me love
You make me vulnerable 

No one knows me like you

You became a light in darker places 
You took the weight off i was bout to cave in 
You helped me more than you know 
You helped me more than you should 

You taught me how to love and stop the hiding 
I hope that I’m enough i’m still deciding
I just don’t want you to go
Cause no one knows me like you 

No one knows me like you
